docs.snippet: RIO DE JANEIRO, Jan. 11-- The Middle Eastern crisis has given a new impetus to the Brazilian Navy's advocacy of a South Atlantic treaty organization. The proposed alliance would be anchored on Brazil and tied to the North Atlantis pact.
